metadata.name: CryptoEth 1
metadata.description:
Immerse yourself in the world of cryptos with this imaginary landscape watercolor and find the hidden references of this world of the future.
Logo are birds, trees hide cryptographic material and more in human-generated architecture.

This genesis piece of the serie is an original 76x56cm watercolor made on Clairefontaine fine grain paper / 300mg
This version is just digitally reworked to enhanced colors

A. Rodicq - 2022
